Euro Weakens Against Dollar on Speculation Over European Short-Selling Ban

-- B y   G r e g   S t o r e y
-- 
2011-08-25T15:03:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-25/euro-weakens-against-dollar-on-speculation-over-european-short-selling-ban.html
The euro weakened against the dollar
and pared gains versus the yen as German stocks fell amid
speculation regulators in France, Spain and  Italy  would extend a
ban on short-selling.  The 17-nation currency traded at $1.4355 and at 111.15 yen
in  New York .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Storey at 
 gstorey@bloomberg.net  